reviews.customers_say: Customers find this sweater well-made and comfortable, noting it's not itchy and has a great weight for autumn temperatures.

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice Quality, Comfortable and Soft
items.body: This is a lightweight, soft sweater that is great for layering. So far, has washed and dried nicely. After washing with the casual cycle, I put it in the dryer on low for 20 minute to get the wrinkles out, then laid it flat to dry the rest of the way. It still looks very nice and had retained its shape. The color is accurate (light blue) and fits as pictured. For reference, I am 5'5, 150# and ordered the size medium. Read more
items.author: Tabitha Kipke

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Comfortable and well made.
items.body: Not too thin or thick. Nice color green. Comfortable and soft. Have bought in other colors. It seems well made. Nice fit. I normally wear a large, that’s what I ordered. It did shrink a little after washing, but that made the fit better. Read more
items.author: Lily Pad

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Cute, Versatile, and Well-Made Sweater
items.body: This sweater was such a fun find! The medium weight fabric makes it perfect for cooler days where it’s warm enough without feeling bulky. The red background with white polkadots gives it a cheerful look that can either go a bit dressy or casual depending on how you style it. So far, the quality seems good with no issues at all. The material feels nice and it’s held up well after a few wears. The sweater is definitely worth grabbing. In fact, I think I will order it in another color as it’s been a great addition to my wardrobe. Read more
items.author: Mindi P

items.title: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great basic sweater looks good and feels good
items.body: Nice sweater but it’s a bit long so I just fold it under so it looks better. I like the polkadots and the fabric feels good against my skin. There are many selections to this style, but I’m a polkadot kind of girl so this is what I chose. Read more
items.author: Hansgirl

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars wonderful sweater
items.body: This is the perfect sweater to wear in fall, spring, or under a heavy coat. It is very lightweight, soft, and comfortable. This is my second one in 2 different colors. Please note that I had to buy one size smaller than normal, and it fit perfectly. Highly recommend. I don't know if it shrinks, but I plan to wash it with warm water and dry flat, as I would wth other sweaters. Read more
items.author: Kindle Customer

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great choice for a knit sweater!
items.body: Super lightweight and great shade of grey! I loved the way it set on my body but for me it did run a bit larger. If purchased again, I would size down. But if a looser fit is what you’re going for - size up! Great for casual jeans and boots, or dressed up with a satin midi skirt. Read more
items.author: Janell Lockhart Ramos

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good fit and warm
items.body: Fits right and looks good. The quality is good. This is a thicker sweater for cold days. Very nice. Read more
items.author: Customer

items.title: 4.0 out of 5 stars This weight is very good. sweater is smooth and comfortable on the skin
items.body: Nice weight, great fit, and very pretty green with black dot pattern. The comfort on the skin is very good, not scratchy at all. Read more
items.author: Customer

short_description:
Womens Maxi Dress Long Sleeve is made for a polished look that still feels comfortable to wear. It is designed to sit cleanly on the body with a flattering shape that works for day plans and dressier moments without feeling overdone.

The fit focuses on balance rather than extremes, so you can move naturally while still getting a defined silhouette. Choose your usual size for a closer look, or size up if you prefer a little more ease through the waist and hips.

Styling is simple: keep accessories minimal for a clean finish, or add a jacket and statement shoes when you want a sharper outfit. This piece photographs well thanks to smooth lines and a structured feel that stays put once you have it adjusted.

With the right fit and simple styling, this item becomes an easy go-to when you want something that looks intentional without requiring extra effort.

Comfort comes from both the cut and the fabric, so selecting your preferred fit makes a noticeable difference over a full day of wear.

This piece transitions well from daytime plans to evening events with a quick change of shoes and a small bag or clutch.

long_description:
Womens Maxi Dress Long Sleeve is a versatile piece you can reach for when you want a put-together look that still feels comfortable. The goal is simple: a silhouette that reads polished, photographs well, and stays wearable for a full day or a long night.

Fit and sizing Fit is where most outfits win or lose. This design aims for a balanced shape with a defined line through the torso, a clean waist, and a smooth finish through the hips and legs. If you prefer a more relaxed feel, size up; if you like a closer fit, stay true to size. Sizes may include: XS, S, M, L, XL.

Fabric and comfort Comfort is not just about softness. It is also about movement and how the fabric behaves as you walk, sit, and stand. A fabric blend with a bit of give helps it keep its shape while still feeling wearable.

Highlights A clean neckline and a refined silhouette for an elevated look. Designed to layer easily with jackets, wraps, or sweaters. Works well with both minimal accessories and statement pieces.

How to style Styling ideas: keep it minimal with neutral shoes and one standout accessory. For a relaxed daytime look, add a denim jacket or cardigan. For events, switch to a bolder shoe and a small clutch for a sharper finish.

Color notes Available colors may include: Brown, Apricot-tz255, Grass Green, Apricot, Army Green, Black, Black-tz256, Coffee, Dark Gray, Orange, Rose Red, Deep Blue, Polka Dot-red, Polka Dot-khaki. If a shade is sold out, check back as availability can change.

Care Care guidance matters if you want it to keep its shape and finish. Follow the label first.
